---
title: Saffron Risotto with Broiled Fennel and Zucchini
description: Golden saffron brings the glamour to this oozy, creamy risotto dish but don't underestimate the fennel! It's fresh, crisp flavour has just a hint of licorice and, combined with the saffron's sweet, aromatic hit, makes this dish very special!
